965
00:41:03,330 --> 00:41:05,430
I have to go.
What?

966
00:42:15,626 --> 00:42:16,996
Why?!

967
00:42:17,066 --> 00:42:19,366
Why did you hurt her?
Why?!

968
00:42:19,436 --> 00:42:23,366
For the first time, I had it.

969
00:42:23,436 --> 00:42:24,936
