00:42:44,656 --> 00:42:46,596
And now?

979
00:42:46,656 --> 00:42:48,826
I'm gonna hurt you.

980
00:42:52,666 --> 00:42:55,796
Get up. Come on.

981
00:42:55,866 --> 00:43:00,136
You do what you have to do, Lucifer.

982
00:43:00,206 --> 00:43:01,406
